description: Tyercoin, developed by the technical team of Tyercoin Entertainment technology company, is an encrypted digital currency based on block chain and intelligent contract technology, which is used in TRC agricultural ecosystem. Tyercoin, as a medium, USES block chain technology to improve traceability and transparency in the agricultural value chain. Set big data cloud computing model analysis, provide intelligent ecological agricultural products supply and quality control to provide efficient solutions. Reduce the cost of agricultural production. Fair pricing to maintain order in the market. Collect actual agricultural data, innovate agricultural production technology, optimize agricultural production, and protect agricultural intellectual property rights and trade agricultural property rights. Combining with agricultural insurance, it can simplify the existing agricultural insurance process very well.
name: Tyercoin
